lead_paragraph: The bodies of Brazilians killed when a plane carrying Chapecoense soccer team crashed in Colombia have all been identified and are being prepared for transport by military aircraft back to Brazil, club Communications Director Andrei Copetti told reporters.

headline.print_headline: Bodies of Brazilians Killed in Colombia Crash Expected Back Friday
